Name: ICA
Description: ICA is one of Sweden's leading retail companies, offering groceries and household items. Stores range from small local shops to large supermarkets.

Name: Coop
Description: Coop is a cooperative retail chain in Sweden that focuses on sustainable and organic groceries.

Name: Willys
Description: Willys is a discount supermarket chain offering low prices and a wide range of products.

Name: Hemköp
Description: Hemköp is a supermarket chain focused on providing fresh and high-quality groceries.

Name: Lidl
Description: Lidl is an international supermarket chain offering high-quality groceries at affordable prices.
